---
title: Quick Sri Lankan Beef & Veggie Curry with Cauliflower Rice & Cashews
description: The aromatic flavours of this beef curry complimented by the richness of tomatoes and the creaminess of light coconut milk will transport
you to the magical streets of Sri Lanka without having to leave your kitchen. With low-carb cauliflower rice, you can enjoy every mouthful
of this beauty without any of the guilt.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
